{"tid":2184611,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"火眼氣膜實驗室邊度合符二級安全水平? 有泄漏危機","createTime":"2020-09-01T16:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T02:52:05.000Z","uid":305261,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"c5549c067aa2d353d72263ebdd119467f2606a41","tid":2184611,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:04:44.000Z","msg":"搵極火眼實驗室個樣都係show個氣膜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但係唔show入面真正處理樣本sample processing/reception嘅位。呢個位先會產生aerosol同splatter，最大風險泄漏SARS-CoV-2<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n終於搵到呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/factstell_/status/1299888328234369026?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffactstell_%2Fstatus%2F1299888328234369026%3Fs%3D19&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=0a7f5ccc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffactstell_%2Fstatus%2F1299888328234369026%3Fs%3D19&h=13d78d40\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/factstell_/status/1299888328234369026?s=19</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NLNOGwt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNLNOGwt.jpg&h=a4f79a91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceehzRt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceehzRt.jpg&h=79edf8c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n班強国專材當工廠咁做，以為塞得越多生物安全櫃(Biosafety cabinet/BSC)越好，但係咁樣做係唔合符標準 (NIH Placement requirements for new buildings and renovations; NSF/ANSI 49 - 2019) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/njq1hgz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnjq1hgz.jpg&h=b7fdaeff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/public-health/services/canadian-biosafety-standards-guidelines/handbook-second-edition/chapter-11-15.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.canada.ca%2Fen%2Fpublic-health%2Fservices%2Fcanadian-biosafety-standards-guidelines%2Fhandbook-second-edition%2Fchapter-11-15.html&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=2a69e276\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.canada.ca/en/public-health/services/canadian-biosafety-standards-guidelines/handbook-second-edition/chapter-11-15.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SCJeCeO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSCJeCeO.jpg&h=66806a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔覺得櫃同櫃之間有3.1m 嘅距離<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁樣會disrupt 個櫃嘅flow pattern, 後面個櫃扯櫃入面嘅空氣出，失去咗保護化驗師嘅功能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LV51hh6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLV51hh6.jpg&h=94dad2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(最common嘅BSC係呢type BSC II a2)<br />\n向下嘅箭咀即係downflow會㩒住啲aerosol，再circulate返櫃後，經過HEPA filter變返乾淨嘅空氣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ry3NXh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRy3NXh5.jpg&h=c966a380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啲氣體係出唔到個櫃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPPtGKK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPPtGKK.png&h=701ffd41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以visualise下扯room air入扯得好勁<br />\n<br />\n跟住佢showcase 個櫃又唔㩒著個櫃，呢個practice都係好危險，如果入面有未清理嘅口水droplet/清得唔好，佢入面啲嘢就真係出晒嚟"},{"pid":"36060756100ee77fe4ff8f8706ddeac384abb18d","tid":2184611,"uid":263577,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"嘩！行內人"},{"pid":"36093e47e6b377ad8349adfa514125d7344dd470","tid":2184611,"uid":36845,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"附近既居民可以做咩去保護自己？"},{"pid":"142663775c250c8529291eb0bcd74a5dc1e9e28a","tid":2184611,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7351849e1431bb19522cb9112f76a970d924293","tid":2184611,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:11:14.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7729095d8a05d1bdcf30249ae8cc75fdec7a8382","tid":2184611,"uid":70771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"幫堆, 太技術向, 普通人會唔明, 但睇黎真係完全冇跟堆standard, 連有冇validation都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef00660d5cc837ecca1a03e300ec46ce1d406dd3","tid":2184611,"uid":13149,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:14:17.000Z","msg":"大陸狗不嬲都係是撚但同亂咁黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db2ec1cda6bcc026103a38be92c3a1bdb859429","tid":2184611,"uid":70771,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"同埋其實佢地唔會理有冇風險, 係香港做危險實驗, 泄漏左咪屈係香港傳出黎, 好似當年SARS咁, 再打造到自己救世主一樣黎打鳩香港, 反正係唔係佢地都會想滅絕真香港人"},{"pid":"a4dc0b969b59fc53abce53b2a62e9a2463a87699","tid":2184611,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:24:44.000Z","msg":"差不多先生"},{"pid":"8ce138cf9d70c5a72f62262dbf35ecd8bce9ec41","tid":2184611,"uid":305261,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"36093e47e6b377ad8349adfa514125d7344dd470","tid":2184611,"uid":36845,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"附近既居民可以做咩去保護自己？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:25:19.000Z","msg":"個BSC嘅牌子係AIRTECH，查下發現好似係強国牌，咩蘇淨安泰公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n理論上所有由BSC輸出嘅空氣都係會經過HEPA filter，過濾晒啲病菌同大過0.3um嘅droplet(帶有病毒)，先出去街外<br />\n但係強国製嘅HEPA filter掂唔掂就唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以要帶口罩 同希望就算出咗街都稀釋晒啦 (感染唔到)"},{"pid":"ab5b7203ddf60d5da04c9c9ebd897862e722f8b2","tid":2184611,"uid":256620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:25:44.000Z","msg":"721.831"},{"pid":"4ab3f056fc6ef377625639682bb75c8169c86951","tid":2184611,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"063a4dbca93d39ec23c9220434e80dc58d4e020d","tid":2184611,"uid":305261,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7729095d8a05d1bdcf30249ae8cc75fdec7a8382","tid":2184611,"uid":70771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"幫堆, 太技術向, 普通人會唔明, 但睇黎真係完全冇跟堆standard, 連有冇validation都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"sorry 講到1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係兩個櫃擺得太近，櫃入面嘅氣流被對面嘅櫃影響，櫃入面空氣有機會漏入實驗室內，感染化驗師，再做成社區感染"},{"pid":"03158fb9b796eec24b2e1cf066b4e682c2a0188b","tid":2184611,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"我要我要 我要健康～"},{"pid":"4dd640cee4c66345e4fa3f547b3a0f804c41fa8d","tid":2184611,"uid":305261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"#save12hkyouth"},{"pid":"10ddaa2aa11336ccb97535b54a2eb386335ad428","tid":2184611,"uid":367090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:52:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，嚟緊會唔會有化驗室群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3039a9ec388e3e70f9e68620c2b21fce231421dd","tid":2184611,"uid":595,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee522ab644aac8314d098d00f25946ae97088391","tid":2184611,"uid":145273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"其實武肺係咪應該入level 3 or 4? 唔應該入level 2"},{"pid":"890894faed604dd9e3cfb5f1a466ecc91d69164d","tid":2184611,"uid":321194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:58:20.000Z","msg":"中學D lab 仲勁D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56089609e98555e80591776c9cea7614fe847ec5","tid":2184611,"uid":265731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:59:50.000Z","msg":"正皮認真刨 spec"},{"pid":"d98006ad111c9de16685bd343679dfebdce27cad","tid":2184611,"uid":61535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:01:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e61a6a042693bf469214b6a75a3161e6f3ffcc3","tid":2184611,"uid":365791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:03:55.000Z","msg":"支那野邊個信，惹到全世界都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee8b6304588f2bd0f91b64d9fbc53235548725c","tid":2184611,"uid":278355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:10:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c90a15a3d0fa1e4a8181b1cea45b0c5412baf03","tid":2184611,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:14:41.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266f17e0ef2b929324eb6c0a7e3f7aca6a6a1fd7","tid":2184611,"uid":305261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3039a9ec388e3e70f9e68620c2b21fce231421dd","tid":2184611,"uid":595,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 